remove `Claimed-by`, append `status closed` log line.

**2h.** `cmdCheck [dir]`: load all tickets + wip map; emit
`VIOLATION <id> <code>: <desc>` for each of:
`claimed-by-not-doing`, `phantom-doing`, `silent-claim`, `ghost-claim`.
Exit 1 if any violations.

**2i.** Extend `validateErg` to return `(errors, warnings []string)`.
Rule 12a: `Claimed-by` on non-doing ticket → error.
Rule 12b: `Status: doing` without `Claimed-by` → warning (exit 0).

**2j.** Wire `claim`, `release`, `close`, `check` in `main()` switch.

